Can someone give me tips about acne scaring? I have acne and after breaking out it almost always leaves pesky hyperpigmentation and scars that literally look like pits. I really do try my best to prevent the scars (e.g. I don’t touch or pop my pimples, I use gentle products to not irritate my skin, no physical exfoliation, etc.) but nothing seems to work and to think that acne scars like that are irreversible is really upsetting. D:
